@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<div class="page-header">
    <h2>✧ About Blazy ✧</h2>
</div>

<div class="about-content">
    <div class="about-section">
        <h3>What is Blazy?</h3>
        <p>Blazy is a nostalgic social media blog platform inspired by the early 2000s internet era. We believe in giving users complete creative freedom to customize their profiles and express themselves uniquely.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <h3>✧ Features ✧</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Custom HTML Profiles:</strong> Personalize your blog with custom HTML, CSS, and backgrounds</li>
            <li><strong>Nostalgic Design:</strong> A throwback to the golden age of personal blogging</li>
            <li><strong>Subscribe to Friends:</strong> Follow your favorite bloggers and never miss a post</li>
            <li><strong>Like & Comment:</strong> Engage with the community through likes, dislikes, and comments</li>
            <li><strong>Tags:</strong> Organize your content with tags and discover new posts</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <h3>♥ Our Mission ♥</h3>
        <p>Blazy aims to bring back the joy of personal expression on the web. In a world of algorithmic feeds and cookie-cutter profiles, we want to give you a space that's truly yours. Customize your profile, share your thoughts, and connect with others in a fun, nostalgic environment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
        <h3>★ Get Started ★</h3>
        <p>Ready to express yourself? <a asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Register now</a> and start customizing your Blazy profile today! Your space, your style, your Blazy.</p>
    </div>
</div>